{"type": "article", "id": 4326, "title": "No Room For Flowers 花瓶", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-12T07:50:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233332bB9CSR2n5rNqf08T.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t比利时艺术创意机构 Case Studyo 近日携手来自纽约布鲁克林的艺术家 Mike Perry 设计了一款名为「No Room For Flowers」的限量版艺术花瓶。No Room For Flowers 尺寸为 9.8 英寸 x 7.8 英寸，选用了白瓷材质手工制作而成，搭配以手绘元素的细节。Mike Perry 在整个花瓶的表面创作了弯曲的线条图案、梯子状图案以及花朵一般模样的眼睛图案，配合着花瓶怪诞的形状，充满奇趣。双方为这款花瓶配置了一款丝网印刷的木箱作为外包装，并且附有 Mike Perry 本人的签名以及限量编号证书，感兴趣的朋友可以<a href=\"http://www.casestudyo.com/2014/12/mike-perry-no-room-for-flowers/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里联系购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233330PVMaAX4idgtNO9wu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233330P3t5vnSOe0ua8xGs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233331qxlgKoNPBZsEp9SQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}